source.name: The Wheat and Barley Scab Initiative
source.description: The goal of the U.S. Wheat and Barley Scab Initiative (USWBSI) is to develop effective control measures that minimize the threat of Fusarium head blight (scab), including the reduction of mycotoxins, to the producers, processors, and consumers of wheat and barley. Community activities are reported here.
